Project 1: Building a Hadoop based information retrieval system

Name: Jinxuan Qu
Email: jinxuaq@g.clemson.edu
Project description:
1. 3 index files
uniword index on package hadoop.jinxuaq.uniword
biword index on package hadoop.jinxuaq.biword
uniword positional index on package hadoop.jinxuaq.uniwordPosition

2. boolean search
Based on uniword index: package hadoop.jinxuaq.booleanSearch
Based on biword index: package hadoop.jinxuaq.biSearch
Based on uniword positional index: package hadoop.jinxuaq.upSearch

3.Interface
Enter search value by using command line in pbs file.
eg: $HADOOP_HOME/bin/hadoop jar $HADOOP_HOME/bi.jar hadoop.jinxuaq.biSearch.Search "scotland and" input/biIndex output/biIndex




